[I] A logic-based symbol placement puzzle

[T] KSudoku is a free version of the popular logic game Sudoku developed by the
[T] KDE community. The game is to fill a nine by nine grid with the numbers
[T] from one to nine filling the rows, columns and three by three squares
[T] without repeating a value on them.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/ksudoku/

